Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.61,0:07:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.26,0:07:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  并没有不安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.79,0:07:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  没有不安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.95,0:07:31.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为一直都有维多利加
