Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:06.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论世界如何改变
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次之后  将再不分离
